Package mph.gui.professor

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArtifactsScreen
    This GUI class contains a list of artifact, it lets the professor evaluate and download each delivered file.
    It extends JFrame.
    NewProjectScreen
    This GUI class lets a professor publish a new project with the desired data and add the deliverables for it.
    It extends JFrame.
    ProfessorMainScreen
    This GUI class lets the professor update his/her personal information and contains the list of the published projects.
    It also lets a professor create a new project to be published.
    It extends JFrame.
    ProjectInfoScreen
    This GUI class contains a tab with the information about the project a tab showing the teams and students enrolled in the project a tab with the requested project deliverables

    It extends JFrame.
